text: This obsoletes IRM 25.23.8 , Campus Exam Identity Theft Case Processing.
It is now obsolete. The material relating to Campus Exam Identity Theft Case Processing is incorporated into IRM 25.23.10 , Compliance Identity Theft Case Processing.
IRM 25.23.8 is obsolete effective the date of this transmittal.
The provisions in this manual apply to all employees working in Identity Theft Victim Assistance - Examination Programs.
